{
  "stem": "15943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they sold the ration of bread to get [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at one point, they sold, again, the bread to get a tangerine on the black market.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that food and the tangerine and the other were on the black market because the, the ghetto government had [INAUDIBLE] to the police and the ones in government.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would get the better rations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they could exchange it or trade it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Usually there was no money trading-- you know, trading for something else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a black market going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sold it for a tangerine, hoping that it's going to save my life again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That took a lot of courage to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- Which brothers were these?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Motele, Moishele, and Laibele.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I was 16, Motele was 14.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Laibele was 13, and Moishele was 11, something within that range.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one time, in fact, we were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This morning, when I got dressed, my brother, well, he was visiting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, well, you don't look like you just came out of Auschwitz, into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I came to Auschwitz wearing a suit because I put on a suit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had an Uncle [NON-ENGLISH] that I [INAUDIBLE], my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was my favorite uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
